sources.title: John Wayne | Rodeo (1934, Western) by Robert N. Bradbury | Colorized Movie
sources.description:
Framed by a gang of murdering thieves!
After stopping a trio of bank robbers, John Weston is tasked by Marshal Higgins to investigate mysterious deaths at the rodeo. Going undercover, he discovers a gang planning to flee with the prize money, putting his life at risk. Will the Man from Utah unmask the criminals in time?

Original title: The Man from Utah (1934) AKA: Rodeo
This film is available with English & Spanish audio, and also subtitles in many languages.

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/D5-XzcsOij4


Director: Robert N. Bradbury
Writers: Lindsley Parsons, Lindsley Parsons
Stars: John Wayne, Polly Ann Young, Anita Campillo & George 'Gabby' Hayes
Genre: Colorized classics, Drama, Western Movie.
